title: JanSport Pack Review: Right Pack
description: With it's signature suede leather bottom, the JanSport Right Pack is the iconic backpack. With an internal 15 inch laptop sleeve and front organizer pocket, the Right Pack is sure to be the best backpack for wherever your day takes you.

asset.author: JanSport

transcripts: Hey guys it's Jayson I'm a senior product developer at jansport and today I'm going to walk you through one of our best selling products the Right Pack. This is one of JanSports classic and timeless backpacks this pack is 31 liters and it's constructed out of a premium quality 915 Denier Cordura and my favorite part super high-quality suede leather bottom. Suede is also found on all the zipper pulls going around to the back of the bag we have a fully padded back panel as well as padded stetch straps and a real quick easy grab haul handle on the top. Going to the main compartment now this is your dump zone for all your books or other items might carry throughout the day it also has a 15-inch laptop compartment. Right so on the front of the pack is a middle compartment with really nice simple organizer panel, it can carry your pens and smaller items, it also has a key clip. And last in the front you have really quick zippered stash pocket here for any other smaller items you might want to carry so that's it for the right pack it's a great pack gets you through the day and as was always lifetime guaranteed.
